Command> glab issue create

TL;DR> create issue

Keywords> gitlab
        > issue


Example01> glab issue create
Example02> glab issue new           # The same as Example01 (alias version)
Example03> glab issue create -m release-2.0.0 -t "we need this feature" --label important
Example04> glab issue new -t "Fix CVE-YYYY-XXXX" -l security --linked-mr 123
Example05> glab issue create -m release-1.0.1 -t "security fix" --label security --web --recover



Reference> https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/cli/-/blob/main/docs/source/issue/create.md
